The '''Guest Towers''' were luxury resorts located on [[Rubyflame Lake]] on [[Centares/Legends|Centares]].<ref name="marvel29">[[Star Wars (1977) 29|''Star Wars'' (1977) 29]]</ref>

After the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] polluted the lake, the Guest Towers were abandoned. They served as hiding place to [[Tyler Lucian]]. It was here [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] [[Death/Legends|killed]] [[Beilert Valance/Legends|Beilert Valance]] shortly before Lucian committed suicide in the lake.<ref name="marvel29" />

